# AI-Based Professional Product Image Generation using JSON Style Extraction

## Task Code

AI-IMG-01

---

# Task Name

AI-Based Professional Product Image Generation using JSON Style Extraction & AI Workflow

---

# Task Summary

This task focused on generating professional ecommerce-style product images using AI image generation workflows and structured JSON-based photography style extraction.

The objective was to analyze professional product photography styles and recreate consistent commercial-quality outputs using structured metadata and prompt engineering techniques.

The project explored:

* Product photography analysis
* JSON-based visual metadata extraction
* AI prompt engineering
* Multi-angle product image generation
* Ecommerce catalog-style presentation
* Texture and lighting consistency

The final outputs included multiple professional product photography perspectives such as:

* Side profile
* Rear view
* Top view
* Outsole view
* Close-up texture shot
* Pair composition
* Three-quarter perspective

---

# Approach

The workflow was implemented using an AI-assisted imaging pipeline.

The process involved:

1. Selecting a professional formal shoe product.
2. Generating multiple product photography angles.
3. Maintaining consistent lighting, framing, shadows, and background composition.
4. Extracting visual characteristics into structured JSON metadata.
5. Using JSON metadata for prompt engineering and style consistency.
6. Producing ecommerce-ready catalog outputs.

The workflow focused on understanding how structured metadata can help AI systems recreate professional photography styles consistently.

---

# JSON Metadata Extraction

The product photography characteristics were converted into structured JSON format containing:

* Product details
* Lighting setup
* Camera angles
* Composition rules
* Texture rendering properties
* Output quality specifications

The metadata helped maintain consistency across all generated outputs.

---

# AI Prompt Engineering

Structured prompts were created using extracted metadata to guide AI image generation.

The prompts controlled:

* Lighting style
* Camera perspective
* Background appearance
* Texture visibility
* Composition quality
* Commercial presentation standards

This improved the realism and consistency of generated images.

---

